description: This file initializes and renders the main React application component into the DOM. It imports React, ReactDOM, global CSS styles, and the main App component, then mounts the React app at the DOM element with id 'root'.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root React element for rendering the app into the DOM.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React component tree into the mounted DOM element.
